content:
[[include :scp-wiki-cn:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]
[[include :scp-wiki-cn:theme:jakstyle]]

[[module CSS]]
:root:lang(cn) {
    --header-title: "ARED";
    --header-subtitle: "异常宗教表现部";
    --lgurl: url("https://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/local--files/hormress-s-logos/ARED_2_i.svg");
    --five-color: 192, 192, 192;
}

div.page-rate-widget-box .rate-points {
    border: none;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    #content-wrap {
        grid-template-columns: none;
    }
}

div.blockquote.warning-panel {
    width: 30rem;
    max-width: 80% !important;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
}

div.blockquote.warning-panel * {
    max-width: 100% !important;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
}

div.blockquote.warning-panel::before {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-image: url("https://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/local--files/hormress-s-logos/ARED_2_i.svg");
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center center;
    background-size: 80% auto;
    opacity: 0.1;
    z-index: 1;
}

div.blockquote.function {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
}

div.blockquote.function > div.image {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    flex-grow: 0;
    margin-right: 1em;
    opacity: 0.2;
}

div.blockquote.function > div.image a {
    box-shadow: none !important;
}

div.blockquote.function > div.content {
    flex-shrink: 1;
    flex-grow: 1;
}
[[/module]]

[[>]]
[[module rate]]
[[/>]]

[[div class="blockquote warning-panel"]]
[[=]]
+ 警告
++ 您正试图访问一份机密文件
此文件（SCP-CN-2820）归属异常宗教表现部全权管理。请确认您拥有异常宗教表现部内部5级许可，任何无授权的继续访问将导致您受到严重违纪处分。
[[/=]]
[[/div]]

[[div style="height: 5rem;"]]
[[/div]]

